title: Udemy 21 Secrets to Build More Self Esteem than a Hollywood Star
description:
Udemy 21 Secrets to Build More Self Esteem than a Hollywood Star Tutorial


This course is going to help you to build and keep your self esteem. The course is made by practical examples and practical lessons.

In this course I included video lessons. Most of them have a practical exercise that I sugest you to do in order to acomplish the course goals.

The course is about 90 minutes. In this 90 minutes I give you a blueprint. Remember: how you implement it depends about you. If you do what I teach you, you'll have huge benefits.


What are the requirements?

-You only have to start this course with an open heart and desire for a better future. I will give you all the other tools.


What am I going to get from this course?

-Over 23 lectures and 1.5 hours of content!
-Make huge progress in short period of time
-Start making real progress in their personal and professional life
-Understand how their self-image interact with their success in every domain
-Change their opinion about themselves
-See themselves as valuable human beings
-Respect their own person for who they are, not for what they have done in the past
-Take imediate control over their state of mind before an interview or something that is challenging

What is the target audience?

-The course if for people who want more in life
-The course if for people who want to overcome fear
-The course is for people who made big mistakes in the past
-The course is NOT for lazy people
-The course is NOT for people who don't want to do anything about their situation
-The course is NOT for people who loves to blame everything and everyone for their failures
